Spb - a textual inteface for Slackware.it Package Browser
==========================================================

This is Spb 2.0.


What is it?
-----------

Spb is a textual interface to the Slackware Package Browser. It is a
Perl script that is capable to query and to fetch packages from the
Slackware mirrors. Spb provides also a reusable Perl module (WWW::SPB).


